{"tid":144966,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)警察故事1-5","createTime":"2017-03-06T00:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T07:44:25.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0cd8556c9e05ce9e6b936c4fd1d4a374e5e75f4","tid":144966,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:56:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpoM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=6114d688\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 按左下可轉CC台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpoM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=f72b9b11\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/fd/Police_Story_(film).jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ffd%2FPolice_Story_%28film%29.jpg&h=54a1b043&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.警察故事內容描述成龍主演的一名警察陳家駒，拘捕了一名毒梟朱滔（楚原飾）。朱滔的女秘書Selina（林青霞飾）成為污點證人，受陳的保護。後來朱滔設計陷害陳，陳被控謀殺，被迫作出反抗證明自己是無辜的..<br />\n<br />\n2.重案組探員陳家駒（成龍飾）因上次的玩命動作眾多，被警隊調往交通部。在調往新職位後，陳家駒向女友阿梅〔張曼玉飾〕表示自己可放下工作包袱，有更多時間見面。可是陳家駒與阿梅之間仍有磨擦，而家駒也因為工作不稱職而自慚，因而決定離開皇家香港警察隊..<br />\n<br />\n3.超級警察陳家駒與楊科長合作做臥底，欲偵破販毒頭目猜霸之巢穴，並取出他存於瑞士銀行的贓款。陳先爭取猜霸頭號手下豹強賞識，豹乃帶他和扮作其妹妹的楊科長到馬來西亞見猜霸。猜霸看重二人敏捷的身手，吩咐他們去救出被大馬政府拘禁的妻子程穎思...<br />\n<br />\n4.曾在越南服兵役的程鋒（于榮光飾），原本在廣州任職護衛，但對工作前景抱有微言。因此鋒找來在香港發展的昔日戰友何炬（林保怡飾），打算到香港一闖。鋒並向任武警的楊建華（楊紫瓊飾）表明賺到錢後，會一同去美國。華勸鋒別急功近利，但鋒稱一心只想著發達，並不聽華的勸告..<br />\n<br />\n5.超級警察陳家駒（成龍）獲CIA委派調查一個國際性核子武器販賣集團，警司驃叔（董驃）與他均以為這是一項簡單任務，怎料，駒在跟踪疑犯徐傑時，誤打誤撞到達了烏黑蘭核子飛彈基地，並目睹傑在雪山與買家交易，駒此時遭對方發現行踪，惟有以雪板展開雪地大逃亡，可惜失足墜進冰湖，幸得俄軍救回一命..<br />\n<br />\n9 30AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da8e9aafe00fe6ce9912ff1c4df0dc72b2fd7ff","tid":144966,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c192ffd2738ebdd57c88ad91194bc2ed3ce59f","tid":144966,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T01:32:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d90fa4bc13a09335123497fd7dc14bfa869e2ec","tid":144966,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T02:11:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6439b74d2dd420c951fdddd8e899da755b1a47d","tid":144966,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T02:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec9e8e590f0f019de1d33eb0c6ec1206636f51c","tid":144966,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40932310497561bad02f1d3f994c4b597a39e67","tid":144966,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T04:18:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e3797292377865df810ac0e0d0eefb307c397a","tid":144966,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,